<p>With time having passed since Lion&rsquo;s release, John and Dave and the entire Mac Geek Gab community have been pooling their knowledge about the benefits &mdash; and pitfalls &mdash; associated with the Snow Leopard-to-Lion upgrade process. Dave and John share some of the latest information here today, as well as some tips about tweaking your Lion-upgraded Mac to behave better. Additionally there&rsquo;s some great Cool Stuff Found included, as well as listener questions answered. Download today and enjoy!</p>
